      "title": "Climate change",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Department of Meteorology has reported occasional rain in Sabaragamuwa province and Kandy and Nuwara Eliya districts.",
        "Upper and North-Western Provinces and Galle and Matara Districts will experience several spells of rain.",
        "Uva, East and North Central Provinces and Mullaitivu District will experience rain or thundershowers at many places during the evening or night.",
        "During thunderstorms, the public is advised to take adequate precautions to minimize damage caused by temporary strong winds and lightning strikes. (R)"
